          </h3>
          <div class="text">
            <lang>
              Beosin provides security audit services for Web3 projects through formal verification
              technology and comprehensive cybersecurity techniques. The audit services cover most
              blockchains including Ethereum, BNB Chain, Polygon, Solana, Polkadot, Aptos, Sui,
              Arbitrum, Near, Cosmos, zkSync. Over 4,000 smart contracts have been audited and
              85,000+ vulnerabilities have been identified.
            </lang>
